SnowBlazer gave a short, impatient sigh. Why had she ever agreed to this 
mission in the first place..? Her violet optics narrowed as she glared at 
Megatron, Rage, and most everyone and everything else in the room "EXCUSE 
me...but I think, you two, that there are more important things to worry 
about then your damned egos.." She turned with a deep throated growl, and 
stalked out. If she wasn't to be answered by their 'commander', who chose to 
instead grapple with another egotistical male on the ship, then she may as 
well see if there were any managable repairs.

~Snowy, the tempermental ^^;;; 

--part1_b8.23f5a7fc.29baa2ec_boundary
